posts.subject: Just want to resolve this
posts.body: Just want to talk to whoever owns that drive, until you do I'll report it and give it to Jess to remove you from Patreon with no refund, all the money you spent will have been wasted right before Christmas.

because the way you are leaking has already got the attention of her knights onn reddit, 3 servers have gone down since yesterday because they are looking for servers again, we had it chill and y'all came in and fucked it up.

don't need a drive, but you need a source, his drive is connected to his email, which is connected to his IP, it's been used before to get rid of leakers and it'll work here. I've got the message ready to go and the report ready to send into both Google and Mega, All I'm asking if to talk to whoever made the drive and see about an alternative that isn't as public and chaotic as this mess of a site

And no, I don't make any money off of her stuff because that's highly illegal and I'm too dumb to pull it off without getting caught. Only person I trust with her content is myself. As proven here, the content posted her leaks out everywhere which means whoever is sourcing her content is at risk of a crack down. Is it really that hard to imagine yet another cosplayer losing their mind and nuking people off os suspicion alone?
Haven't leaked publicly in about a year now, once we left zeronet originally I stopped being public about it.

Yes, I've talked to him as well about it, and he isn't sharing to servers that leak it everywhere, I just told him about how his links are being used to spread around the leaks and he's going to look into who did it

Because of my past, if she goes crazy, an old leaker will get nuked the same as new leakers. I want to stay in the tier now and open leaks are making that much more difficult. I have no say in who she removes from her Patreon which means that if she decides to just remove people off of suspicion, I'm fucked along with everybody else that's joined her Patreon in the past few months
If I get nuked I'll just have more time on my hand to be here dumbass, plus I'll have nothing to lose by reporting every leak out there.

not a waste of time, might be a redemption attempt if that's what it comes too. just saying, I want to talk to whoever made the drive, if they don't want to talk then I'll just report them as they come up. Can't ban me from seeing the content posted here so it's get your source reported, or have a conversation
weird, but serious. At the very least this site needs to get locked down and people don't need to know about it. If everybody knows about it, Nigri knows about it then
